    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ASR Outdoor mini-folding pocket tool is a must-have everyday carry tool! It sports a classic style that looks great and will keep you prepared for anything on the go without taking up too much space. These utility tools feature 3 essential functions you can utilize throughout the day - mini scissors, a bottle opener, and a nail cleaner which should cover all the basics of your multi-tool needs. Measuring just 2.5” in length, it will easily fit in just about any pocket and comes with a practical key ring for multiple storage and carry capabilities. Made of durable, corrosion-resistant 420 stainless steel, you can count on this pocket multi-tool for everyday use and even during inclement weather</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 3 Function Classic Starter Pocket Utility Multi-Tool Camping Outdoor</h2>\n  <p>The ASR Outdoor mini-folding pocket tool is a must-have everyday carry tool! It sports a classic style that looks great and will keep you prepared for anything on the go without taking up too much space.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>CLASSIC UTILITY STARTER - Folding pocket multi-tool sports a classic style that looks great and keeps you prepared on the go; keep a handy tool on you at all times without too much bulk</li>\n    <li><strong>MULTI-FUNCTION TOOL - 3 essential tool functions include:</strong> mini scissors, bottle opener, nail file; covering all the basics of your multi-tool pocket needs</li>\n    <li>COMPACT DESIGN - Measuring just 2.5” long, the pocket tool fits anywhere and comes with a practical key ring for multiple storage and carry capabilities; hang from a keychain or belt loop for quick and easy access</li>\n    <li>DURABLE CONSTRUCTION - Made of corrosion-resistant 420 stainless steel that won’t rust; Count on this compact multi-tool for everyday use and during inclement weather</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - Material:</strong> 420 stainless steel; Open length: 3.58”; Closed length: 2.28”; Weight: .045lbs (.72oz); Colors: orange, grey, blue; 3 functions: bottle opener, scissors, nail cleaner</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72016/6i0JKoDnHNPvz8y1DnoDma7lDYyWas-metabWluaS1rbmlmZS12YXJfZml4ZWQuanBn-.jpg\" alt=\"The ASR Outdoor mini-folding pocket tool is a must-have everyday carry tool\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASR5UTILPK</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058466938</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>These utility tools feature 3 essential functions you can utilize throughout the day - mini scissors, a bottle opener, and a nail cleaner which should cover all the basics of your multi-tool needs. Measuring just 2.5” in length, it will easily fit in just about any pocket and comes with a practical key ring for multiple storage and carry capabilities.</p>\n  <p>Made of durable, corrosion-resistant 420 stainless steel, you can count on this pocket multi-tool for everyday use and even during inclement weather. Make sure to grab one of these to keep on you whether you’re camping, hiking, or just going about your day in case you need it!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
